features: ETL Safety Standard Test Inspected and Certified. O’ Bright LED Pharmacy Desk Lamp is safe for daily use.

Energy Saving, Super Bright LED light. Good for Work/End Tables with built in high efficient 12 Watt LEDs. Approximately 50,000 hours of lifespan. No replacement bulbs needed. LEDs deliver a maximum of 1050 Lumens of brightness which is equal to 75W incandescent bulbs. You can save up to 80% of your electricity bill when compared to halogen and incandescent lighting.

Smart Dimming/Memory allows you to find your preferred light intensity with our full range dimming feature. The Dimmable memory Function enables you to find the desired lighting and keep it there through power ups. Simply press the power button once to turn on/off then press and hold to find the brightness you are looking for. You can achieve a high brightness setting for craft work in addition to a soft brightness for mood lighting or reading.

Ultra-Flexible Design allows for a unique fit to your décor. The 270° swivel head allows for mood lighting (upward tilt) or direct light for work (downward tilt). The Swivel Head has a convenient arm to make adjusting the O’ Bright Pharmacy Desk Lamp swivel head seamless. Take your lighting a step further with the 360° swing arm capability.

The Durable and Classic Vintage Design of the Pharmacy Desk Lamp is composed of 100% metal. You can smoothly rotate the lamp in any desired direction with safety and ease. Inspire your workspace with the retro look of brushed nickel and the classic vintage design.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great lamp and great price
reviews.reviewText: This lamp exceeds all expectations. It is well designed, attractive in any setting, and best of all-it is so functional. It arrives in highly protective, packaging, and it is extremely easy to assemble. The ability to dim the light is also a positive. I don’t know if this is a recommendation or not, but I’m getting ready to order my second lamp today.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Such a great buy! Easy to assemble. The black lamp looks elegant on our black electric Casio stand-up piano. Since this piano doesn't have any space behind the music sheet stand, we needed light source that has a heavy base and a long arm so the light can shine over the center of a music book. (And, bonus, if we want extra room light we rotate this light fixture upward to bounce off the wall and ceiling, so it can double as a floor lamp.) The feature that it remembers the brightness setting from when it was turned off is also great--no need having to reset the preferred brightness each time it's turned on.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Superb Design & Quality
reviews.reviewText: Exact to its description, and exceeds my expectations. You'd think that any ole desk lamp would do -- not so. Many are too lightweight to stand sturdily, or made in such a way that the pole and extensions loosen and sag over time. I haven't had this for long, but I am confident by its design, components, and assembly that it will hold up. The adjustable position of the extension apparatus and overall light is ideal. The base never has to move to reposition the light. As a bonus, the intensity of the light's brightness is adjustable. Easy on; easy off. All this, and it's attractive and a great price. I bought this for my home office. I'm requisitioning the purchase of 6 more for our business office. And, I'll buy my son one for his apartment. Keeper.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars WOW .. what a great lamp!
reviews.reviewText: Just unpacked this yesterday. Shipping was prompt. It was well packed, and extremely easy to put together. The base is nice and heavy to keep the lamp stable. I'm using it for a reading lamp on an end table in the living room. It can be dim, or extremely bright. It is a 'warm' light color ...not that 'greyish' light color like some LEDs. I like that it has a slim profile, so it looks really nice, and not big and clutzy. Very pleased with this lamp !

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I only gave this lamp 4 stars because it doesn't have the presence that I thought it would have, although its very cute and retro. It's a great little lamp, works well, and I ended up using it in a different area in the house that called for a small lamp. Good value.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars One of my two favorite lamps
reviews.reviewText: Have used for a while now and absolutely love it. It’s sturdy, made well, plenty bright enough when needed and can be dimmed to a pleasant soft glow that still permits working without eye strain. I have it on my home office desk and have received many compliments. Its attractive and modern-traditional appearance would work with multiple decor styles in many different rooms.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love this lamp
reviews.reviewText: I am so glad I ordered this lamp. It is a perfect bedside reading lamp…….I really like the gradual dimmer or brightening aspect and the movable arm and tilting shade to get the light in just the right position. I also think it looks pretty cool. If you need a good bedside or desk lamp give this one a try!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Came in damaged
reviews.reviewText: I loved the light, however, it came in with 2 pieces not capable of being attached to each other. I returned for a refund and decided to keep looking . Otherwise, the lamp was good looking and easy to assemble.

reviews.reviewTitle: Excellent product - wish you could give a more accurate delivery time
reviews.reviewText: Use it on a bureau in my entryway
Busque lámparas por mucho tiempo. Me importaba el nivel de brillo y flexibilidad de posición. Pesa un poco, me la imaginé más ligera, pero vale la pena. Tiene muchas opciones de posición y dimmer.
